Hellpeon growls as it watches Attila dodge his blasts. He prepares to 
open fire again when he hears the whistling sound of missiles and 
turns around to see Incarcinators right infront of him. All three 
collide with him and cause a massive explosion to come about then 
some autogun blasts and all 25 of Atillas shots strike the energy 
being while it is surrounded in the flame of the missiles. As the 
smoke and fire clear, Hellpeon  seemingly floats there with a huge 
hole in his stomach as well as some in his arms and legs. The beast 
roars as it outstretches its arms and the wound in his stomach begins 
to regenerate hastily as the holes in his arms dissapear all 
together. The beast looks to Attilla as its eyes glow a bright red. 
Quickly the beast flys over to him and opens fire on him with 10 
beams of chaochitan energy until he is in a fairly close distance...
